item.title: By: Ken Stanley
item.dc:creator: Ken Stanley
item.description: Great stuff indeed and I always commend innovation. However, apart from the fact that it's free and no account is required, it's just a scaled down version of <a href="http://www.conceptshare.com/" rel="nofollow">Concept Share</a>. Nevertheless, give the man the tickets.
